(196, 6, 2, 'Naina Devi Temple', 'One of the prominent Shakti Peethas, situated atop a hill offering panoramic views. The temple is dedicated to Goddess Sati and is particularly crowded during Navratri celebrations.', 'Naina Devi Temple.jpg', 'Location: 31.3052Â° N, 76.5364Â° E (Bilaspur District)', 'â€¢	Temple Trust Sarai â€¢	Hotel Lake View â€¢	HPTDC Rest House â€¢	Budget hotels in Bilaspur', 'https://srinainadevi.com/', 'â€¢	Gobind Sagar Lake â€¢	Bilaspur Town (25 km) â€¢	Bhakra Dam (30 km) â€¢	Rewalsar Lake (80 km)', 'â€¢	Temple Langar â€¢	Lake View Restaurant â€¢	Local dhabas â€¢	Bilaspur restaurants', 'â€¢	Nearest Airport: Chandigarh (100 km) â€¢	Railway Station: Kiratpur Sahib (40 km) â€¢	Regular HRTC buses from Bilaspur and Chandigarh â€¢	Ropeway facility available'),
